74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-%C3%BD-ki%C3%AAm-tr%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-Mai-S%C6%A1n-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-_K4rRb6p8E9GviTEENnJSg">Thuật ý kiêm trình hữu nhân Mai Sơn Phủ - 述意兼呈友人枚山甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/Ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0-thu%E1%BB%B7-k%C3%BD/poem-8WwuSop69rG9-aoxa8C2nQ">Tiên trà thuỷ ký - 煎茶水記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/author-MfG9Dcv0CtbGpIaXvmxDnA">Trương Hựu Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/Ti%E1%BB%83u-ph%E1%BB%A5-bi%E1%BB%87t-th%C3%AC-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-BUIL_DU5XfRJRrtYzMUprg">Tiểu phụ biệt thì kỳ 2 - 小婦別時其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZqGaWwKOrJXGaqhA3jlDaw">Viên Hoằng Đạo</a>)<br></div>	</div>
